            <h1>About Book Haven Bookstore</h1>
            <img src="bookstore-interior.jpg" alt="Book Haven Bookstore interior showing cozy reading areas" width="600" height="300">
            
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded in 2004 by literary enthusiast Sarah Mitchell, Book Haven Bookstore has been a beloved cornerstone of our community for over two decades. What started as a small dream to create a space where book lovers could gather, discover new authors, and engage in meaningful literary discussions has grown into a thriving independent bookstore that serves readers of all ages.</p>
            
            <p>Our mission is simple: to foster a love of reading and learning in our community while providing exceptional customer service and carefully curated book selections. We believe that books have the power to transform lives, spark imagination, and bring people together.</p>

            <h2>What Makes Us Special</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Curated Selection:</strong> Every book in our store is hand-selected by our knowledgeable staff</li>
                <li><strong>Personal Service:</strong> Our team provides personalized book recommendations based on your interests</li>
                <li><strong>Community Events:</strong> We host regular author readings, book clubs, and literary events</li>
                <li><strong>Cozy Atmosphere:</strong> Comfortable reading nooks and a welcoming environment for all</li>
                <li><strong>Local Authors:</strong> We proudly support and showcase local writers and their works</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
            <div>
                <div>
                    <img src="staff-sarah.jpg" alt="Sarah Mitchell, Owner" width="150" height="150">
                    <h3>Sarah Mitchell</h3>
                    <p>Owner & Founder</p>
                    <p>Sarah's passion for literature led her to open Book Haven in 2004. She specializes in contemporary fiction and poetry.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="staff-james.jpg" alt="James Rodriguez, Assistant Manager" width="150" height="150">
                    <h3>James Rodriguez</h3>
                    <p>Assistant Manager</p>
                    <p>With a background in library science, James excels at helping customers find exactly what they're looking for.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="staff-emily.jpg" alt="Emily Chen, Events Coordinator" width="150" height="150">
                    <h3>Emily Chen</h3>
                    <p>Events Coordinator</p>
                    <p>Emily organizes our author events and book clubs. She's particularly knowledgeable about young adult literature.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
